90286e0 Jonas Fonseca 2013-10-14 14:56 -0400  25|   )
90286e0 Jonas Fonseca 2013-10-14 14:56 -0400  26|
90286e0 Jonas Fonseca 2013-10-14 14:56 -0400  27|   lazy val benchmarkSettings = defaultSettings ++ Seq(
